{0 Ocsigen Server}

Ocsigen Server is a full-featured Web server. It implements most features of
the HTTP protocol, and has a powerful extension mechanism that makes it easy to
plug in new functionalities. Many extensions are available, such as a reverse
proxy, an access control mechanism, content compression, etc.

